# Pipeline — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

Stages flow left to right. A ticket moves forward manually; it can be sent back to any prior stage.

| Stage | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| New | Opened, not yet triaged |
| Open | Triaged and actively being worked |
| Awaiting Quote | Scoped; waiting on a quote or the contact's go-ahead before work starts |
| Waiting | On contact reply, third party, or internal decision |
| Blocked | Cannot proceed — external dependency or unresolved impediment |
| Resolved | Fix or answer delivered; awaiting contact confirmation |
| Closed | Done |

